org.dmd.util
Class IntegerVar

java.lang.Object
  org.dmd.util.IntegerVar
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>
public class IntegerVar
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>

The IntegerVar class provides for the storage of a integer value that can be changed. This allows for a reference to an integer to be passed and alterred. It also allows for the alteration of an integer value object without having to create a new Integer.
